467
00:31:59,927 --> 00:32:01,565
"Årstiden for tåge...

468
00:32:01,647 --> 00:32:05,117
og moden frugtesløshed."

469
00:32:05,207 --> 00:32:08,279
Jeg elsker Keats!
Kender du det her?

470
00:32:08,367 --> 00:32:10,403
